info.name: VinFast API (VN)
info.description:
Collection for VinFast Connected Car API. 

**Setup**:
1. Import this collection.
2. Set the `email` and `password` variables in the Collection Variables tab.
3. Run requests in order: Login -> Get Vehicles -> Get Aliases -> Get Telemetry.
